  "rationale": "<p>Choice D is correct. Factor: (30<i>q</i> &minus; 5)<i>x</i> = 60. For no solution, the coefficient of <i>x</i> must equal 0 while the right side does not: 30<i>q</i> &minus; 5 = 0, so <i>q</i> = 1/6.</p><p>Choices A, B, and C produce equations that do have solutions.</p>",
